Localization.Name: APX Fire Extinguisher
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: KE Group
Item Type: Fire Extinguisher
Class: Gadget

Magazine Size: Gas Canister
Rate of Fire: Constant
Effective Range: 3-4 m

The KE Group's APX Fire Extinguisher has been rated a best-in-class consumer grade safety equipment for well-over a decade making it the industry standard in fire prevention. Filled with a patented gaseous cooling compound, the extinguisher can rapidly smother any fire in sight. The digital screen on the device allows you to monitor the local temperature to help you contain and eliminate fire hazards.

Localization.Name: Greycat Industrial
Localization.Description: A trusted manufacturer of industrial tools since 2337, the company’s extensive line of industrial equipment and armor make it one of the most respected brand names around. Greycat has remained a UEE staple for centuries thanks to their streamlined-yet-inventive designs, exacting safety standards, and a diverse product line.
